Summary

Dataset: Malawi

Outcome variable: EGMA quantity discrimination at Endline (quant1 - quant10)

Comparison variable: Gender (Male, Female)

Items with no variance: none

Items with no variance within levels of comparison variable: none

Bias detection method: IRT

Total number of biased items: 0 out of 10

Type of item bias: NA

No DIF was detected by IRT. Therefore, robustness checks of treatment effects were not performed.
